SUMMARY:Cabin Getaway · Petaluma KOA Resort — Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:Rent a cozy Deluxe Cabin (real beds\, full bath) for an easy 
 first overnight close to home. Your little guy can meet goats\, mini donk
 eys\, and horses at the petting farm\, bounce on the giant jumping pillow
 \, splash in the pool\, and roast a first marshmallow by the fire.\nDrive
 : ~1 hr 10 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://koa.com/campgrounds/san-fra
 ncisco/
LOCATION:San Francisco North Petaluma KOA Resort\, 20 Rainsville Rd\, Pet
 aluma CA
URL:https://koa.com/campgrounds/san-francisco/
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
