DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260727
SUMMARY:Splash Zone at The Wave (Emerald Glen Park) — Dublin
DESCRIPTION:The Wave's Splash Zone is a zero-depth water-play area made f
 or little ones — a tipping bucket\, a shallow pool\, gentle sprays and sq
 uirters\, and two kiddy slides. The perfect first water-play day. Open su
 mmer season\; buy waterpark admission.\nDrive: ~25 min from Fremont\nWebs
 ite: https://www.thedublinwave.com
LOCATION:The Wave Waterpark Dublin CA
URL:https://www.thedublinwave.com
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
