SUMMARY:Habitot Children's Museum — Berkeley
DESCRIPTION:A museum designed specifically for ages 0–5: their first art 
 easel\, first water table\, soft climbing blocks\, and a toddler-safe cra
 wl tunnel. Everything is squishy\, washable\, and made for tiny explorers
 .\nDrive: ~45 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://www.habitot.org
LOCATION:Habitot Children's Museum Berkeley CA
URL:https://www.habitot.org
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
