SUMMARY:Cabin Getaway · Evergreen Lodge at Yosemite — Groveland
DESCRIPTION:A two-bedroom family cabin tucked in the pines near Yosemite 
 — room to put the little guy to bed while you relax on the deck. A big sh
 allow-end saltwater pool\, a forest playground\, an indoor toddler play r
 oom\, nature crafts\, and s'mores by the fire. Book early for summer.\nDr
 ive: ~2 hr 45 min from Fremont\nWebsite: https://www.evergreenlodge.com
LOCATION:Evergreen Lodge at Yosemite\, 33160 Evergreen Rd\, Groveland CA
URL:https://www.evergreenlodge.com
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
